Package com.w10.risk_game.utils.maps

Class MapAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.w10.risk_game.utils.maps.DominationMapDriver
      • com.w10.risk_game.utils.maps.MapAdapter
  • public class MapAdapter
extends DominationMapDriver
    The MapAdapter class is a Java class that acts as an adapter between the DominationMapDriver and ConquestMapDriver classes, allowing for the translation of game maps between the two formats.
